The time between events,
the space between particles,

00:11:02.380 --> 00:11:06.160 align:middle line:10%
the silence between
thoughts or sounds

00:11:06.160 --> 00:11:10.540 align:middle line:10%
is the emptiness
between expressions.

00:11:10.540 --> 00:11:13.180 align:middle line:84%
Rather than focusing on
the expressions themselves,

00:11:13.180 --> 00:11:15.430 align:middle line:90%
focus on the gap.

00:11:15.430 --> 00:11:18.610 align:middle line:84%
The quantum gap is more
fundamental than the particles

00:11:18.610 --> 00:11:20.740 align:middle line:90%
or events themselves.

00:11:20.740 --> 00:11:24.070 align:middle line:84%
The gap is like the blank
canvas or empty space

00:11:24.070 --> 00:11:28.180 align:middle line:84%
