And this is the
final bridge, what

00:11:42.340 --> 00:11:45.220 align:middle line:90%
I call the expansion bridge.

00:11:45.220 --> 00:11:48.900 align:middle line:90%
It's the quantum access point.

00:11:48.900 --> 00:11:50.910 align:middle line:84%
And with this
expansion bridge, we

00:11:50.910 --> 00:11:55.290 align:middle line:84%
