am into the void.

00:11:55.290 --> 00:11:59.610 align:middle line:90%
We come into I am nothing.

00:11:59.610 --> 00:12:05.250 align:middle line:84%
I am empty of all things, and I
surrender to that nothingness.

00:12:05.250 --> 00:12:07.830 align:middle line:90%


