We become one with
all that is, and we

00:12:20.880 --> 00:12:25.140 align:middle line:90%
move into I am all things.

00:12:25.140 --> 00:12:29.010 align:middle line:90%
I am the limitless light.

00:12:29.010 --> 00:12:35.430 align:middle line:84%
Now how do we transition through
the gap to come into oneness?

00:12:35.430 --> 00:12:37.350 align:middle line:84%
Throughout this journey
of consciousness,

00:12:37.350 --> 00:12:40.470 align:middle line:84%
we've been stimulating
the central nervous system

00:12:40.470 --> 00:12:42.240 align:middle line:90%
in different ways.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:45.540 align:middle line:10%
But this final step of
the expansion bridge

00:12:45.540 --> 00:12:49.200 align:middle line:10%
is about taking
away the stimulation

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:55.230 align:middle line:10%
and coming into stillness,
silence, and emptiness.

00:12:55.230 --> 00:12:59.130 align:middle line:90%
We surrender to that stillness.

00:12:59.130 --> 00:13:03.300 align:middle line:84%
This contrast sets us free
from the bounds of the body,

00:13:03.300 --> 00:13:06.970 align:middle line:84%
allowing us to expand
into the universe.

00:13:06.970 --> 00:13:10.620 align:middle line:84%
It's a surrendering, but it
takes a lot of discipline

00:13:10.620 --> 00:13:13.410 align:middle line:90%
to come to that stillness.

00:13:13.410 --> 00:13:17.250 align:middle line:84%
We surrender in order to
pass through the gateway

00:13:17.250 --> 00:13:18.810 align:middle line:90%
of the zero.

00:13:18.810 --> 00:13:21.360 align:middle line:90%
We come to nothingness.

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:25.980 align:middle line:84%
Our sense of time
and space disappear.

00:13:25.980 --> 00:13:30.480 align:middle line:84%
We enter into the gap between
the moments of expression.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:33.130 align:middle line:90%


00:13:33.130 --> 00:13:35.890 align:middle line:84%
Our journey through these
three major energy centers

00:13:35.890 --> 00:13:38.890 align:middle line:84%
of the upper, middle,
and lower tanden

00:13:38.890 --> 00:13:42.190 align:middle line:90%
prepares us for this final step.

00:13:42.190 --> 00:13:45.370 align:middle line:84%
We bring our conscious
awareness from the mind

00:13:45.370 --> 00:13:47.750 align:middle line:84%
into the deepest
parts of our body,

00:13:47.750 --> 00:13:52.490 align:middle line:84%
connecting to that deep
stillness at the hara.

00:13:52.490 --> 00:13:55.550 align:middle line:10%
Once we connect at
the hara, we weave

00:13:55.550 --> 00:13:58.110 align:middle line:10%
this energy back
up to the heart,

00:13:58.110 --> 00:13:59.990 align:middle line:10%
then again to the third eye.

00:13:59.990 --> 00:14:04.250 align:middle line:84%
And this closes the loop like
the symbol of the ouroboros,

00:14:04.250 --> 00:14:07.560 align:middle line:84%
or the serpent
biting its own tail.

00:14:07.560 --> 00:14:10.380 align:middle line:84%
In doing this, we are
weaving the energy

00:14:10.380 --> 00:14:13.500 align:middle line:84%
and activating this whole
circuit of the three

00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:17.010 align:middle line:90%
major energy centers.

00:14:17.010 --> 00:14:20.190 align:middle line:84%
From a Kabbalistic perspective,
these three energy centers

00:14:20.190 --> 00:14:24.750 align:middle line:84%
correspond with Yesod, Tif'eret,
and Keter on the middle pillar

00:14:24.750 --> 00:14:26.590 align:middle line:90%
of the Tree of Life.

00:14:26.590 --> 00:14:30.360 align:middle line:84%
So we're activating the
middle pillar in this process.

00:14:30.360 --> 00:14:34.380 align:middle line:10%
We're opening up the way to
the supernal realm, where

00:14:34.380 --> 00:14:37.860 align:middle line:10%
we may experience
unity consciousness,

00:14:37.860 --> 00:14:42.820 align:middle line:10%
and then back down to flow this
light into our mind and body.

00:14:42.820 --> 00:14:46.650 align:middle line:84%
This is a state of being
that is fully in tune

00:14:46.650 --> 00:14:49.620 align:middle line:90%
and aligned with source.

00:14:49.620 --> 00:14:51.960 align:middle line:84%
But in order to
reach that unity,

00:14:51.960 --> 00:14:56.880 align:middle line:84%
we must surrender our
attachment to self-identity.

00:14:56.880 --> 00:14:59.370 align:middle line:84%
The biggest attachment
we tend to have

00:14:59.370 --> 00:15:02.680 align:middle line:90%
is often to our own identity.

00:15:02.680 --> 00:15:06.240 align:middle line:84%
We fear losing ourself
if we were to fully

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:09.820 align:middle line:90%
let go and enter into the void.

00:15:09.820 --> 00:15:16.290 align:middle line:84%
But this surrender is key to
finding our one true self that

00:15:16.290 --> 00:15:21.770 align:middle line:84%
is far more vast than the
personal self-image we hold.

00:15:21.770 --> 00:15:24.980 align:middle line:84%
We move beyond
the personal self,

00:15:24.980 --> 00:15:30.270 align:middle line:84%
moving from I am
something to I am nothing.

00:15:30.270 --> 00:15:33.770 align:middle line:84%
And once we surrender, we
then have the opportunity

00:15:33.770 --> 00:15:36.860 align:middle line:84%
to experience the
unlimited potentials

00:15:36.860 --> 00:15:38.960 align:middle line:90%
of the zero-point field.

00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:45.606 align:middle line:84%
We surrender so that we may come
into oneness with all things.

00:15:45.606 --> 00:15:48.720 align:middle line:84%
Now the biggest
challenges we face here

00:15:48.720 --> 00:15:52.950 align:middle line:84%
are often our fear of the
unknown, our resistance

00:15:52.950 --> 00:15:58.770 align:middle line:84%
to letting go of control, and
our discomfort with silence.

00:15:58.770 --> 00:16:01.410 align:middle line:84%
If we want to
access the void, it

00:16:01.410 --> 00:16:06.450 align:middle line:84%
is key that we bring our
mind and body to stillness.

00:16:06.450 --> 00:16:11.340 align:middle line:84%
We eliminate stimulation
and quiet our inner self

00:16:11.340 --> 00:16:15.000 align:middle line:90%
by relaxing more deeply.

00:16:15.000 --> 00:16:20.910 align:middle line:84%
The void is a non-visual,
non-auditory experience.

00:16:20.910 --> 00:16:25.380 align:middle line:84%
It's a simultaneous sense
of oneness, allness,

00:16:25.380 --> 00:16:27.480 align:middle line:90%
and emptiness.

00:16:27.480 --> 00:16:32.370 align:middle line:84%
The moment we think any thought
or are stimulated in some way,

00:16:32.370 --> 00:16:34.740 align:middle line:90%
we're drawn out of it.

00:16:34.740 --> 00:16:38.760 align:middle line:84%
Often, we might not even
realize we were in the void

00:16:38.760 --> 00:16:41.980 align:middle line:90%
until we shift back out.

00:16:41.980 --> 00:16:45.720 align:middle line:84%
Connecting with the void
requires a letting go

00:16:45.720 --> 00:16:49.440 align:middle line:90%
of control and expectation.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:51.600 align:middle line:90%
We cannot control this process.

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:54.990 align:middle line:84%
We can only open
up and allow it.

00:16:54.990 --> 00:17:00.330 align:middle line:84%
It's a surrendering of the mind
and the self into the unknown

00:17:00.330 --> 00:17:03.810 align:middle line:90%
of the void, into nothingness.

00:17:03.810 --> 00:17:08.829 align:middle line:84%
But the experience of expanding
and surrendering to the void,

00:17:08.829 --> 00:17:11.280 align:middle line:84%
it's not a one time
experience after which

00:17:11.280 --> 00:17:13.800 align:middle line:90%
we're forever more enlightened.

00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:18.450 align:middle line:84%
Rather, the void is always
here, right here, right now,

00:17:18.450 --> 00:17:20.589 align:middle line:90%
right in front of you.

00:17:20.589 --> 00:17:23.460 align:middle line:84%
And when we establish
the pathways,

00:17:23.460 --> 00:17:27.540 align:middle line:84%
we can cross this bridge
as often as we like.

00:17:27.540 --> 00:17:31.500 align:middle line:84%
We can access the gaps
between the moments and tune

00:17:31.500 --> 00:17:35.576 align:middle line:84%
into the zero-point
field of quantum reality.

00:17:35.576 --> 00:17:39.280 align:middle line:84%
Now what do we do if
we tap into the void,

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:44.020 align:middle line:84%
but we can't seem to hold it
for more than a few seconds?

00:17:44.020 --> 00:17:45.340 align:middle line:90%
Not to worry.

00:17:45.340 --> 00:17:48.220 align:middle line:84%
Even a brief time in
the void connects us

00:17:48.220 --> 00:17:51.790 align:middle line:84%
with vast potential energy
and flows this energy

00:17:51.790 --> 00:17:54.490 align:middle line:90%
into our personal consciousness.

00:17:54.490 --> 00:17:58.300 align:middle line:84%
And any time you find yourself
slipping out of it, just

00:17:58.300 --> 00:18:01.750 align:middle line:84%
connect to your hara
and your breath.

00:18:01.750 --> 00:18:05.320 align:middle line:84%
The hara is an access
point to the void.

00:18:05.320 --> 00:18:09.990 align:middle line:84%
If the mind gets distracted, the
energy doesn't flow properly.

00:18:09.990 --> 00:18:14.140 align:middle line:84%
So to reconnect, we bring
our attention to the hara.

00:18:14.140 --> 00:18:18.250 align:middle line:84%
We focus on our breath,
breathing in and out

00:18:18.250 --> 00:18:20.470 align:middle line:90%
through the lower tanden.

00:18:20.470 --> 00:18:24.970 align:middle line:84%
And this brings us
back into the void.

00:18:24.970 --> 00:18:29.870 align:middle line:84%
Once we connect with the
void, we must surrender.

00:18:29.870 --> 00:18:32.050 align:middle line:90%
Let go of our mind.

00:18:32.050 --> 00:18:34.390 align:middle line:90%
Let go of our thoughts.

00:18:34.390 --> 00:18:37.270 align:middle line:90%
Surrender to the stillness.

00:18:37.270 --> 00:18:40.660 align:middle line:84%
As we do, we allow
ourselves to pass

00:18:40.660 --> 00:18:43.510 align:middle line:84%
through this gateway
that then connects

00:18:43.510 --> 00:18:46.180 align:middle line:90%
to the limitless light.

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:48.910 align:middle line:84%
Now what does this
all mean for us?

00:18:48.910 --> 00:18:52.350 align:middle line:90%
What's the big picture here?

00:18:52.350 --> 00:18:55.260 align:middle line:84%
When we connect to the
void, the quantum field

00:18:55.260 --> 00:18:58.650 align:middle line:84%
of all possibilities
becomes available to us

00:18:58.650 --> 00:19:01.020 align:middle line:90%
so that we can observe it.

00:19:01.020 --> 00:19:05.670 align:middle line:84%
When we hold this state,
miracles are possible.

00:19:05.670 --> 00:19:10.740 align:middle line:84%
We access our full potential
to create miracles to manifest

00:19:10.740 --> 00:19:13.350 align:middle line:90%
and to defy logic.

00:19:13.350 --> 00:19:17.760 align:middle line:84%
Ultimately, we are raising
up to our individuated self,

00:19:17.760 --> 00:19:23.760 align:middle line:84%
the true self, transcending
ego rather than denying it.

00:19:23.760 --> 00:19:27.300 align:middle line:84%
It's a process of alchemy
to transmute and transform

00:19:27.300 --> 00:19:29.490 align:middle line:90%
into a more pure state.

00:19:29.490 --> 00:19:32.190 align:middle line:84%
And this is the
process of ascension.

00:19:32.190 --> 00:19:35.550 align:middle line:84%
And in this process,
there is sacrifice.

00:19:35.550 --> 00:19:40.890 align:middle line:84%
We are offering our attachments,
our ego, our personality

00:19:40.890 --> 00:19:44.400 align:middle line:90%
onto the altar of sacrifice.

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:48.420 align:middle line:84%
But in truth, we're sacrificing
the lesser for the greater.

00:19:48.420 --> 00:19:51.450 align:middle line:84%
It's an act of
surrender and devotion.

00:19:51.450 --> 00:19:53.070 align:middle line:84%
We're letting go
of the distortions

00:19:53.070 --> 00:19:56.310 align:middle line:84%
so the true self
can shine through.

00:19:56.310 --> 00:20:00.800 align:middle line:84%
And we are becoming the true
magician, or the Adam Kadmon.

00:20:00.800 --> 00:20:04.820 align:middle line:84%
In the tarot, this archetype
is represented by the magician.

00:20:04.820 --> 00:20:07.950 align:middle line:10%
And the magician stands
as the middle pillar,

00:20:07.950 --> 00:20:10.830 align:middle line:10%
with one hand reaching
up to source and one hand

00:20:10.830 --> 00:20:13.260 align:middle line:10%
reaching down to the physical.

00:20:13.260 --> 00:20:17.730 align:middle line:10%
He is the conduit in perfect
alignment with divine will.

00:20:17.730 --> 00:20:21.690 align:middle line:10%
And there is a level of
purity, and he is actively

00:20:21.690 --> 00:20:25.360 align:middle line:10%
stepping into that
role to be the conduit.

00:20:25.360 --> 00:20:28.340 align:middle line:10%
He's engaging his
will to align so

00:20:28.340 --> 00:20:29.970 align:middle line:10%
that the pure
energies from source

00:20:29.970 --> 00:20:34.360 align:middle line:10%
can flow through
without distortion.

00:20:34.360 --> 00:20:37.920 align:middle line:84%
This is not a
reactive posture but

00:20:37.920 --> 00:20:42.960 align:middle line:84%
actively stepping into
alignment to be in the flow.

00:20:42.960 --> 00:20:46.230 align:middle line:84%
The magician directs the powers
of heaven and the universe

00:20:46.230 --> 00:20:49.230 align:middle line:84%
into the physical,
into the four elements,

00:20:49.230 --> 00:20:52.350 align:middle line:84%
according to an
intention that is set.

00:20:52.350 --> 00:20:55.290 align:middle line:84%
And to achieve this
purity, the negative ego

00:20:55.290 --> 00:20:59.580 align:middle line:84%
must be surrendered so that
it doesn't distort the energy

00:20:59.580 --> 00:21:02.340 align:middle line:90%
coming through to manifest.

00:21:02.340 --> 00:21:05.670 align:middle line:84%
At this level, we can
accomplish and perform magic.

00:21:05.670 --> 00:21:08.820 align:middle line:84%
We can make things happen,
while not getting too caught

00:21:08.820 --> 00:21:11.490 align:middle line:90%
up or attached to the process.

00:21:11.490 --> 00:21:16.410 align:middle line:84%
We maintain our state of
balance on the middle pillar.

00:21:16.410 --> 00:21:19.260 align:middle line:84%
The only way to
stay in tune with it

00:21:19.260 --> 00:21:23.220 align:middle line:84%
is to continue, starting
each day with connection

00:21:23.220 --> 00:21:25.480 align:middle line:90%
to stillness.

00:21:25.480 --> 00:21:28.480 align:middle line:84%
We connect with
the source first.

00:21:28.480 --> 00:21:32.120 align:middle line:84%
And then we flow
that through our day.

00:21:32.120 --> 00:21:35.110 align:middle line:84%
And as we step into action,
we become the conduit

00:21:35.110 --> 00:21:38.950 align:middle line:84%
to allow that source energy to
flow through us in alignment

00:21:38.950 --> 00:21:40.480 align:middle line:90%
with higher will.

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:42.400 align:middle line:90%
It's very active.

00:21:42.400 --> 00:21:44.970 align:middle line:90%
And it's a choice we make.

00:21:44.970 --> 00:21:48.220 align:middle line:84%
Now to connect with
that state of stillness,

00:21:48.220 --> 00:21:51.970 align:middle line:84%
start by sitting or
standing upright.

00:21:51.970 --> 00:21:54.800 align:middle line:90%
Then focus on your breath.

00:21:54.800 --> 00:21:57.680 align:middle line:90%
Inhale through the nose.

00:21:57.680 --> 00:22:00.930 align:middle line:90%
Exhale through the mouth.

00:22:00.930 --> 00:22:03.710 align:middle line:84%
Pull the breath all the
way down to the hara,

00:22:03.710 --> 00:22:06.650 align:middle line:90%
just below your navel.

00:22:06.650 --> 00:22:13.580 align:middle line:84%
Continue to focus on this point
as you breathe in and out.

00:22:13.580 --> 00:22:16.890 align:middle line:90%


00:22:16.890 --> 00:22:22.010 align:middle line:84%
Now slow your breathing down
using the following technique.

00:22:22.010 --> 00:22:24.800 align:middle line:84%
Breathe in to a count of
five in through the nose.

00:22:24.800 --> 00:22:28.050 align:middle line:90%


00:22:28.050 --> 00:22:31.790 align:middle line:10%
Hold your breath here in the
hara for a count of five,

00:22:31.790 --> 00:22:32.990 align:middle line:10%
holding it down here.

00:22:32.990 --> 00:22:35.630 align:middle line:90%


00:22:35.630 --> 00:22:37.857 align:middle line:84%
Then breathe out
to a count of 10,

00:22:37.857 --> 00:22:39.190 align:middle line:90%
breathing out through the mouth.

00:22:39.190 --> 00:22:43.550 align:middle line:90%


00:22:43.550 --> 00:22:45.290 align:middle line:84%
Continue this
breathing technique

00:22:45.290 --> 00:22:48.890 align:middle line:84%
until you feel yourself
dropping into a deeper

00:22:48.890 --> 00:22:51.260 align:middle line:90%
state of stillness.

00:22:51.260 --> 00:22:56.060 align:middle line:84%
You can even extend the time of
the pause between the inbreath

00:22:56.060 --> 00:22:57.188 align:middle line:90%
and the outbreath.

00:22:57.188 --> 00:23:00.260 align:middle line:90%


00:23:00.260 --> 00:23:04.280 align:middle line:84%
Focus on the gap, the
stillness between the breaths.

00:23:04.280 --> 00:23:07.450 align:middle line:90%


00:23:07.450 --> 00:23:11.150 align:middle line:84%
As you feel your sense
of self dissolving

00:23:11.150 --> 00:23:15.320 align:middle line:84%
and your mind becomes
like a quiet pond,

00:23:15.320 --> 00:23:17.440 align:middle line:84%
you can gently
then drop your head

00:23:17.440 --> 00:23:23.640 align:middle line:84%
down a little bit into the space
just in front of your face.

00:23:23.640 --> 00:23:26.340 align:middle line:84%
But don't try to do that
until you really feel

00:23:26.340 --> 00:23:29.010 align:middle line:90%
that sense of self dissolving.

00:23:29.010 --> 00:23:34.320 align:middle line:84%
So until then continue to focus
on this breathing technique.

00:23:34.320 --> 00:23:37.540 align:middle line:84%
Then once you do
drop your head down,

00:23:37.540 --> 00:23:40.950 align:middle line:84%
hold this position while
allowing your breath

00:23:40.950 --> 00:23:43.522 align:middle line:90%
to now become more still.

