a morning affirmation

00:24:04.430 --> 00:24:07.220 align:middle line:90%
that we use every day.

00:24:07.220 --> 00:24:11.180 align:middle line:84%
I come out of the
darkness into the light.

00:24:11.180 --> 00:24:14.000 align:middle line:90%
I come with nothing.

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:16.820 align:middle line:90%
I know nothing.

00:24:16.820 --> 00:24:19.100 align:middle line:90%
I am empty of all things.

00:24:19.100 --> 00:24:21.740 align:middle line:90%


00:24:21.740 --> 00:24:24.730 align:middle line:84%
And then we tap
into that emptiness.

00:24:24.730 --> 00:24:29.500 align:middle line:84%
And only when we can be
empty and be the no thing,

00:24:29.500 --> 00:24:33.940 align:middle line:84%
