gate into the all things.

00:24:33.940 --> 00:24:39.930 align:middle line:84%
And then, therefore, I am
ready to receive all things.

00:24:39.930 --> 00:24:43.410 align:middle line:84%
And we tap into the limitless
light that flows directly

00:24:43.410 --> 00:24:44.805 align:middle line:90%
from source to us.

00:24:44.805 --> 00:24:47.490 align:middle line:90%


00:24:47.490 --> 00:24:51.360 align:middle line:84%
Ultimately, this journey is
about becoming the Adam Kadmon,

00:24:51.360 --> 00:24:55.230 align:middle line:84%
the perfected human, and
reaching our full potential

00:24:55.230 --> 00:24:57.720 align:middle line:90%
as multidimensional beings.

00:24:57.720 --> 00:25:01.590 align:middle line:90%
This is who we truly are.

